44
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:45,300
<font color="yellow">Meskipun aku melakukannya, dia hanya terus tidur, seperti mayat!</font>

45
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:49,000
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kau lakukan kepada kakakku? Hah?</font>

46
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,500
<font color="yellow">Nona Yoo Rim. Tenanglah, dan--</font>

47
00:03:51,500 --> 00:03:53,599
<font color="yellow">Tenangkan saja pantatmu sendiri, kau bajingan!</font>

48
