<font color="yellow">Aku bangun.</font>

49
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,100
<font color="yellow">Ini terlalu pagi!</font>

50
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:27,199
<font color="yellow">Kenapa aku bangun sangat pagi?</font>

51
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:35,000
<font color="yellow">Jumat? Aku tertidur selama dua hari?</font>

52
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:37,100
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun, aku pasti sudah gila!</font>

53
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:53,000
<font color="yellow"><i>Apa kau mau menerimanya?</i></font>

54
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:57,800
<font color="yellow">Yang aku butuhkan hanya kau, nona Hye Rim.</font>

55
